OL,3,CGP who tried to kill mother's partner
OL,4,Cwith poison jab jailed for 31 years
OL,6,FA GP has been jailed for more than 30
OL,7,Fyears for trying to kill his mother's
OL,8,Fpartner with a fake Covid jab loaded
OL,9,Fwith poison while posing as a
OL,10,Fcommunity nurse.
OL,12,FDr Thomas Kwan was sentenced at
OL,13,FNewcastle Crown Court on Wednesday (6
OL,14,FNovember) having previously pleaded
OL,15,Fguilty to the attempted murder of
OL,16,FPatrick O'Hara.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/14
