OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F423A1730909438
OL,3,CGP who tried to kill mother's partner
OL,4,Cwith poison jab jailed for 31 years
OL,6,FIn an elaborate plot described as
OL,7,Fbeing "like something out of a
OL,8,FHollywood movie", the 53-year-old
OL,9,Fhatched a plan to kill the long-term
OL,10,Fpartner of his mother in a bid to cut
OL,11,Fhim out of her will.
OL,13,FThe unsuccessful scheme saw Kwan send
OL,14,Ffake NHS letters and texts before
OL,15,Fdressing in disguise and administering
OL,16,Fa fake Covid booster which would leave
OL,17,Fhis 72-year-old victim with lifelong
OL,18,Fmental and physical injuries.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/14
