OL,4,Cwith poison jab jailed for 31 years
OL,6,FWhen January came, another fake letter
OL,7,Fwas sent to Mr O'Hara informing him a
OL,8,Fhome visit with a nurse had been
OL,9,Farranged.
OL,11,FThis was followed by a text message
OL,12,Freminding Mr O'Hara of the
OL,13,Fappointment, the day before the attack.
OL,15,FIn the early hours of 22 January, Kwan
OL,16,Fmade the journey from his home in
OL,17,FBrading Court, Ingleby Barwick, to
OL,18,FNewcastle, using fake registration
OL,19,Fplates on his car.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/14
