OL,3,CGP who tried to kill mother's partner
OL,4,Cwith poison jab jailed for 31 years
OL,6,FKwan came before a jury charged with
OL,7,Fattempted murder but admitted his
OL,8,Fguilt on the second day of trial last
OL,9,Fmonth.
OL,11,FPaul Greaney KC, defending Kwan,
OL,12,Fpreviously told the court there were
OL,13,F"mixed motives" behind the attempted
OL,14,Fmurder.
OL,16,FMr Greaney said: "This terrible scheme
OL,17,Fdid not have as its sole focus
OL,18,Ffinancial gain but was much more
OL,19,Fgenerally influenced by his feelings
OL,20,Fabout his relationship with his mother
OL,21,Fand the way she had treated him.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G12/14
