OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F423A1730909438
OL,3,CGP who tried to kill mother's partner
OL,4,Cwith poison jab jailed for 31 years
OL,6,F"It's not just financial gain, other
OL,7,Fthings are happening."
OL,9,FMr Greaney added: "There is little to
OL,10,Fextenuate offending as grave as this.
OL,12,F"He is entitled to ask you to take
OL,13,Finto account the fact he, at the age
OL,14,Fof 53, has no previous convictions,
OL,15,Fthe fact he is a local GP and he
OL,16,Fshould be regarded as having been of
OL,17,Fpositive good character and thirdly it
OL,18,Fis plain he is not going to have an
OL,19,Feasy time in prison."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G13/14
