OL,4,Cwith poison jab jailed for 31 years
OL,6,FMr Greaney said probation officials
OL,7,Fhad assessed Kwan posing a "medium
OL,8,Frisk to his own mother".
OL,10,FKwan was sentenced to 34 years
OL,11,Fimprisonment, reduced to 31 years and
OL,12,Ffive months on account of his guilty
OL,13,Fplea. He will serve two thirds of the
OL,14,Fsentence behind bars.
OL,16,FDuring sentencing, Mrs Justice Lambert
OL,17,Fsaid Kwan was not considered to be a
OL,18,Frisk to the wider public and therefore
OL,19,Fdid not hand him the life sentence the
OL,20,Fprosecution had called for.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G14/14
